OL,3,CLondon 'the most expensive place to
OL,4,Cdie' according to funeral cost report
OL,6,FLondon remains the most expensive
OL,7,Fplace to die, with the cost of a
OL,8,Fsimple attended funeral averaging
OL,9,F#4,897.
OL,11,FSunLife's latest Cost of Dying Report
OL,12,Falso revealed the cost of a
OL,13,Ftraditional attended funeral jumped
OL,14,F5.3% with rising prices driven by
OL,15,Fincreased cremation and burial fees,
OL,16,Fhigher coffin prices, and increased
OL,17,Fliving costs.
