OL,3,CLondon 'the most expensive place to
OL,4,Cdie' according to funeral cost report
OL,6,FSome 15% of families say they have
OL,7,Ffaced financial hardship paying for a
OL,8,Ffuneral, having to find an extra
OL,9,F#2,365 on average.
OL,11,FMore than one in 10 (12%) of those
OL,12,Ffacing financial difficulty turned to
OL,13,Fcrowdfunding to cover funeral costs,
OL,14,Fwhile 8% reported borrowing money from
OL,15,Fan unregulated lender or loan shark.
