OL,3,CLondon 'the most expensive place to
OL,4,Cdie' according to funeral cost report
OL,6,FSunLife chief executive Mark Screeton
OL,7,Fsaid: "Funerals are a deeply personal
OL,8,Fexperience, but our research shows
OL,9,Fthat the cost of saying goodbye
OL,10,Fcontinues to rise faster than some
OL,11,Ffamilies can afford.
OL,13,F"We are seeing more people turning to
OL,14,Fsimple attended funerals, a modern
OL,15,Fmiddle ground between traditional and
OL,16,Fdirect options, allowing families to
OL,17,Fcelebrate their loved one's life
OL,18,Fwithout overspending.
